==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Deplumation
<hw>Dep`lu*ma"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Deplumate</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The stripping or falling off
of plumes or feathers.</def> <rj><au>Bp. Stillingfleet</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A disease of the eyelids, attended
with loss of the eyelashes.</def> <rj><au>Thomas.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deplume</ent>⟦br⟧
